  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Weapon Type: Ranged Firearm</p><p>The ninja from the Land of the Sky use this type of projectile weapon.</p><p>When using this weapon, a barrage of kunai will be fired at high speeds in a similar fashion to machine guns.</p><p>This weapon has the Two-Handed, Finesse, Loading, and Ammunition properties (its ammunition must be 1 stack of kunai).</p><p>When you take the attack action using this weapon, all creatures in a 30-foot cone extending from you must make a Dexterity saving throw against your Taijutsu Save DC, taking 8d4 + your ability modifier piercing damage on a failed save, or half as much on a success.</p><p></p>",
